    "cost_rationale": "Three-subtask plan: (1) mongo_query (mid) to fetch Slack contract renewals from SAM with aggregation on renewal dates and license counts. (2) sql_gen (mid) to extract consumption metrics from warehouse—straightforward time-series aggregation of usage over the renewal window. (3) cross_recon (frontier) to reconcile the two sources and classify renewal trajectory; frontier tier assigned because this requires multi-signal reasoning to align contract commitments against actual consumption patterns, infer posture (oversized/undersized), and generate actionable renewal recommendations. The cross_recon step is a single subtask because classification and trajectory recommendations are inherent to the reconciliation task, not separate policy or downstream steps."
